OL,3,CHopes that wild beavers could return
OL,4,Cto waterways after hundreds of years
OL,6,FThe return of wild beavers to
OL,7,Fwaterways hundreds of years after they
OL,8,Fwere hunted to extinction in the UK
OL,9,Fhas taken a step closer with the
OL,10,Fapproval of a test project.
OL,12,FSheffield councillors recently
OL,13,Fapproved spending #98,000 on a study
OL,14,Fon introducing beavers to Blacka Moor
OL,15,Fand the surrounding Upper Don
OL,16,FCatchment as part of natural flood
OL,17,Fdefence plans for the area.
