OL,3,CHopes that wild beavers could return
OL,4,Cto waterways after hundreds of years
OL,6,FThe study is being funded by a
OL,7,FYorkshire Regional Flood and Coastal
OL,8,FCommittee Capital Grant and by
OL,9,FYorkshire Water.
OL,11,FThis will provide the opportunity to
OL,12,Fexamine whether the reintroduction of
OL,13,Fbeavers is feasible close to a major
OL,14,Fcity, where thousands of homes and
OL,15,Fbusinesses are at risk of flooding.
