OL,3,CHopes that wild beavers could return
OL,4,Cto waterways after hundreds of years
OL,6,FDams created by would slow down the
OL,7,Frate of water flow from the large
OL,8,Fupland areas. This would have the
OL,9,Fpotential to help safeguard Sheffield,
OL,10,Fplus Rotherham and Doncaster
OL,11,Fdownstream, from flooding.
OL,13,FCouncillor Marieanne Elliot, who has
OL,14,Fbeen leading work to respond to the
OL,15,Fnature emergency it called five years
OL,16,Fago, visited a project in North
OL,17,FYorkshire last August and was
OL,18,Fimpressed by what she saw.
