OL,3,CHopes that wild beavers could return
OL,4,Cto waterways after hundreds of years
OL,6,FShe said that beavers help
OL,7,Fbiodiversity because their presence
OL,8,Fcreates a mosaic of habitats and this
OL,9,Fallows more species to thrive.
OL,11,FWhen beavers fell trees to build dams,
OL,12,Fthey don't kill them, so the trees
OL,13,Fwill coppice and regrow.
OL,15,FCoun Elliot said: "Securing the
OL,16,Ffunding for a beaver feasibility study
OL,17,Fin Sheffield is really exciting. I
OL,18,Fwent to visit a project in North
OL,19,FYorkshire that's five years in, and
OL,20,Fcould see how the beavers have
OL,21,Fpositively changed the landscape.
