OL,3,CHopes that wild beavers could return
OL,4,Cto waterways after hundreds of years
OL,6,FShe said: "As trees are felled and
OL,7,Fwetlands created, other plant species
OL,8,Femerge. Beavers bring wood into the
OL,9,Fwater, that wood provides food and
OL,10,Fshelter for insects. Those insects
OL,11,Fbecome food for other species.
OL,13,F"The project I visited had more bats,
OL,14,Fherons, kingfishers, dragonflies,
OL,15,Fotters, owls and much more frogspawn,
OL,16,Fas a result of the beavers being
OL,17,Fthere."
